            <div class="post-content-inner">
              
              Linus comes from a different generation of developer and an older, freer time on the internet, before everyone had to pretend to be nice to everyone.  And you know, he's Linus Torvalds, he ain't got to explain it.<br /><br />FFS, Microsoft wrote the software that made it a household name back when its developers would get into profanity-laden screamfests during meetings.  There's something to be said for just getting everything out of your system, then going out for a beer with the person you just had a knock-down with.

              

              
              
            </div>
